    " NOTE: Additional iTerm2 mapping: Control + Option + Delete
    inoremap <M-t><M-g><M-i><M-o> <C-g>u<C-w>
    " Control + Option + d: Delete word forward
    inoremap <M-t><M-g><M-o><M-i> <Esc>ldwi

